        <item>
            <title>张家朗 IG 被意大利人洗版闹偷金牌　意大利剑击联盟为赛果提抗议</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/cheungkalong-ig-spam-by-italian/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cheungkalong-ig-spam-by-italian</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/cheungkalong-ig-spam-by-italian/hottopic/spotlight/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:23:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[运动科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[2024 巴黎奥运]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[张家朗]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1253662</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">香港剑击选手张家朗今日成功在 2024 巴黎奥运的男子花剑个人项目再度夺金，是花剑 68 年历史以来首次有剑手成功衞冕金牌。不过张家朗在决赛面对的意大利剑手马治（Filippo Macchi）和他的团队却对赛果感到不满，认为他被剥夺了应得的金牌，意大利剑击联盟亦表明会向国际剑联及国际奥委会提出抗议。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253670 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mfile_1763780_1_2024-e1722318392232-626x580.jpg" alt="" width="626" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mfile_1763780_1_2024-e1722318392232-626x580.jpg 626w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mfile_1763780_1_2024-e1722318392232-972x900.jpg 972w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mfile_1763780_1_2024-e1722318392232.jpg 1451w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 626px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1763780-20240730.htm">RTHK</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">张家朗在花剑决赛中与对手马治难分难解，多次出现比数追平的情况，直到最后出现「决三剑」的情况下张家朗成功以 15:14 胜出。其中最争议的地方就在于「决三剑」，来自台湾的国际裁判在头两次的判决中均判定了需要重打，直到第三次才判决张家朗取得决胜分胜出赛事。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="it" dir="ltr">Filippo Macchi argento per incompetenza.<br />Oro per l&#39;intervista post partita.<br />Oro pure a Stefano Cerioni come c.t.<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Macchi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Macchi</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Cerioni?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Cerioni</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/fencing?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#fencing</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Olimpiadi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Olimpiadi</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Olympics?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Olympics</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/OlimpiadiParigi2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#OlimpiadiParigi2024</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/olimpiadi2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#olimpiadi2024</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/OlympicGames?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#OlympicGames</a><a href="https://t.co/99YM5x6b1S">pic.twitter.com/99YM5x6b1S</a></p><p>&mdash; eletizia (@chiamamimirella) <a href="https://twitter.com/chiamamimirella/status/1818035952310485124?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">July 29, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">意大利剑击联盟质疑两位分别来自台湾和南韩的裁判质素不符合比赛水平，又指有裁判是来自香港的邻近地区，认为任何情况下裁判都不会是来自邻近的国家或地区。香港前花剑代表张小伦同样认为裁判的判决有问题，他提到几剑都是张家朗占上风，而且判决只会是其中一方成功得分，而不可能是重打。他认为裁判的判决很犹豫，对两位剑手都会造成很大的影响。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="wp-image-1253665 size-medium aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2097-320x580.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2097-320x580.jpg 320w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2097.jpg 496w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 320px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class=" wp-image-1253673 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2100-694x218.jpg" alt="" width="523" height="164" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2100-694x218.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2100.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 523px" /></p><figure id="attachment_1253674" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1253674" style="width: 485px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1253674 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2101-485x580.jpg" alt="" width="485" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2101-485x580.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2101.jpg 752w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 485px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1253674" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲意大利网民在张家朗 IG 上洗版攻击</span></figcaption></figure><p>其实不只马治和他的团队对赛果感到不满，战线更转移至网络上。不少意大利网民在赛果一出后，纷纷涌到张家朗的 Instagram 帐户中「洗版」，攻击张家朗偷走了他们的奥运金牌。他们在张家朗的 IG 留下了「以他为耻」、「偷走了奥运奖牌」、「依靠法国教练关系取胜可耻」等的恶意留言。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253677 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2102-316x580.jpg" alt="" width="316" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2102-316x580.jpg 316w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2102.jpg 490w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 316px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253678 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2103-317x580.jpg" alt="" width="317" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2103-317x580.jpg 317w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2103.jpg 492w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 317px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class=" wp-image-1253679 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2104-586x580.jpg" alt="" width="343" height="339" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2104-586x580.jpg 586w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2104.jpg 909w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 343px" /></p><figure id="attachment_1253666" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1253666" style="width: 318px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1253666 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2099-e1722318023373-318x580.jpg" alt="" width="318" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2099-e1722318023373-318x580.jpg 318w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2099-e1722318023373-494x900.jpg 494w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2099-e1722318023373.jpg 1168w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 318px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1253666" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲香港网民以「菠萝 Pizza」还击</span></figcaption></figure><p style="font-weight: 400;">当然香港网民不会放任自己的选手被人这样攻击，大多数支持张家朗的网民都认为意大利团队输打赢要，挺身向张家朗表示支持并用上意大利人最讨厌的菠萝披萨「🍍」、「🍕」Emoji 还击。但都有网民劝停有关的留言还击，避免为张家朗的成功沾上污点。</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.i-cable.com/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A/%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/254424/?utm_source=facebook_cable_news&amp;utm_medium=facebook_link_organic&amp;utm_campaign=share&amp;fbclid=IwY2xjawEVTdlleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHRGoW4fbn3sEB-C6hGJigUXQ3Z4kCxHp7X8pZskpuyYG5pOyoZ0KwV6-Wg_aem_NTrm20IyfZ6qrtmi-c-7Qw">有线新闻</a></span></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1763768-20240730.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/summer-olympics-apple-maps-update/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Maps 推出更新，为巴黎奥运揭幕作准备</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/cheungkalong-ig-spam-by-italian/hottopic/spotlight/">张家朗 IG 被意大利人洗版闹偷金牌　意大利剑击联盟为赛果提抗议</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
