        <item>
            <title>【实试】AI 单凭图片定位真的准确吗？ 测试不同国家风景相 AI 分析能力</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/29/geospyai-photo-location-prediction-ability-test/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=geospyai-photo-location-prediction-ability-test</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/29/geospyai-photo-location-prediction-ability-test/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 13:00:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GeoSpy AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[看图定位]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1249620</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">你有想像过 AI 单凭照片的背景就能够精准地定位出照片在哪里拍摄的吗？GeoSpy 正正就具备着这一个功能，据说其准确度相当之高，接下来将会为大家测试一下究竟 GeoSpy 是否真的能如此准确地从照片的细节就分析出拍摄地点。我将会使用来自两个不同国家的 2 张风景相，3 张来自网上的风景相以及 3 张香港的风景相，来测试 GeoSpy 是不是真的能精准地为照片定位。</p><h2>泰国</h2><figure id="attachment_1249653" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249653" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249653 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/thai1-694x527.jpg" alt="泰国" width="694" height="527" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/thai1-694x527.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/thai1.jpg 1186w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249653" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲成功定位于泰国的芭堤雅</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1249654" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249654" style="width: 575px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249654 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/thai2-575x580.jpg" alt="泰国" width="575" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/thai2-575x580.jpg 575w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/thai2.jpg 893w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/thai2-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 575px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249654" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲同样成功定位曼谷</span></figcaption></figure><p>我使用了两张在泰国旅游时用来告诉朋友自己所在地点方便集合的照片来测试，GeoSpy 只用了不到十秒的时间就已经成功将照片定位于对应的芭堤雅和曼谷。根据 GeoSpy 的描述，它是根据照片中文字的语言以及建筑的结构、路牌和树木来判断照片的位置。不得不说 GeoSpy 的定位能力十分强大，只是其提供的坐标却完全不是照片的实际拍摄地方，但当时随便拍下的照片竟然都能被定位到泰国，GeoSpy 的表现依旧令我很惊讶。</p><h2>日本</h2><figure id="attachment_1249703" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249703" style="width: 593px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249703 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gundam1-593x580.jpg" alt="台场" width="593" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gundam1-593x580.jpg 593w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gundam1.jpg 921w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 593px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249703" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲定位成功但照片背景有明显线索</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1249704" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249704" style="width: 593px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249704 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gundam2-593x580.jpg" alt="台场" width="593" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gundam2-593x580.jpg 593w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/gundam2.jpg 921w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 593px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249704" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲将线索都遮蔽后同样能成功定位</span></figcaption></figure><p>我将在日本台场拍摄的实物独角兽高达同样放上 GeoSpy 上定位，能精准地将照片定位在台场，而提供的坐标虽然不是独角兽高达的确切坐标，但同样是位于台场。由于照片属于热门景点，而且照片背景有明显的文字显示了旁边商场的名字，所以我将可能会向 GeoSpy 提供额外线索的文字和招牌都遮盖，最后 GeoSpy 同样能精准定位并提供了位于台场的坐标。</p><figure id="attachment_1249689" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249689" style="width: 615px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249689 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-9-615x580.jpg" alt="日本" width="615" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-9-615x580.jpg 615w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-9.jpg 955w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 615px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249689" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲只得路灯和樱花的背景依然能成功定位</span></figcaption></figure><p>我尝试将照片定位难度升级，将一张只有街灯和樱花为背景的照片上传至 GeoSpy，GeoSpy 竟然也能将照片定位于日本东京，虽然坐标仍然是错误的，但它能依靠樱花就能分析出这张照片是在春天时在东京拍摄。</p><h2>网上</h2><figure id="attachment_1249782" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249782" style="width: 624px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249782 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/5-4-624x580.jpg" alt="GeoSpy" width="624" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/5-4-624x580.jpg 624w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/5-4.jpg 968w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 624px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249782" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲成功定位于西班牙的奎尔公园</span></figcaption></figure><p style="text-align: center;">照片来源：<a href="https://www.kkday.com/zh-tw/blog/15050/europe-spain-barcelona-must-visit">KKday</a></p><figure id="attachment_1249781" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249781" style="width: 624px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1249781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-6-624x580.jpg" alt="GeoSpy" width="624" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-6-624x580.jpg 624w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-6.jpg 968w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 624px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249781" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲成功定位于德国的罗腾堡</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1249783" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249783" style="width: 667px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249783 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-4-667x580.jpg" alt="GeoSpy" width="667" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-4-667x580.jpg 667w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-4.jpg 1035w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 667px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249783" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲成功定位于奥地利的圣史蒂芬大教堂</span></figcaption></figure><p style="text-align: center;">照片来源：<a href="https://www.leo-travel.idv.tw/">Travel with Leo</a></p><p>我从网上搜寻了来自西班牙、德国和奥地利三个国家的热门景点照片，GeoSpy 非常成功地定位三张照片中的景点建筑，虽然当中的坐标并非十分精准但是也没有相差很远，其中圣史蒂芬大教堂的坐标更是完全正确。</p><h2>香港</h2><figure id="attachment_1249793" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249793" style="width: 672px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249793 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-7-672x580.jpg" alt="GeoSpy" width="672" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-7-672x580.jpg 672w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-7.jpg 1042w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 672px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249793" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲能定位在香港，但地点错误</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1249794" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249794" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249794 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/5-5-694x566.jpg" alt="GeoSpy" width="694" height="566" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/5-5-694x566.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/5-5.jpg 1103w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249794" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲成功定位于大澳</span></figcaption></figure><p>以上的照片分别是观塘海滨和大澳，GeoSpy 成功将照片都定位在香港，但它未能分析出第一张照片是来自观塘海滨，第二张照片则能透过大涌桥上色彩鲜艳的旗帜和旁边的建筑分析出是大澳，但其中的坐标依然错误。</p><figure id="attachment_1249723" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249723" style="width: 687px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249723 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-17-687x580.jpg" alt="" width="687" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-17-687x580.jpg 687w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-17.jpg 1066w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 687px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249723" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲错误定位在理工大学</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1249721" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1249721" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1249721 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-12-694x481.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="481" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-12-694x481.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-12.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1249721" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲坐标定位是浸会大学</span></figcaption></figure><p>GeoSpy 成功从后面海报架中捕捉到「The Hang Send University of Hong Kong Graduation Ceremony 2023」的字眼，但却错误地将照片定位于在红磡的理工大学，最奇怪是其分析得出的坐标竟是位于九龙塘的浸会大学。</p><h2>总结：目前较适用于热门景点</h2><p>GeoSpy 看图定位的能力测试后的确是十分厉害，基本上照片大致所在的国家/地区都能成功分析，只是具体照片确切是位于什么地方就未必能够做到了。GeoSpy 工具在分析一些非常热门的地方或景点时非常有用，可以快速且准确地定位到所在地，但由于 GeoSpy 是以照片的光线、植物、建筑风格、天气等线索再对比大量的街景和地理照片来进行分析，所以像是一些非常随意拍摄的照片或是没有太多线索的照片可能 GeoSpy 就发挥不到效用了。目前 GeoSpy 仍处于免费开放使用的测试阶段，相信得到更多的数据后其看图定位的能力将会再有提升。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/29/geospyai-photo-location-prediction-ability-test/ai/">【实试】AI 单凭图片定位真的准确吗？ 测试不同国家风景相 AI 分析能力</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
